A commercial motorcyclist and his passenger have been crushed to death by a Toyota Hilux at the Ozoro/Kw√†le expressway in Delta State. It was learnt that the Toyota Hilux was on a very high speed when it failed brake, lost control and hit the motorcycle from behind. The motorcyclist and his passenger died on the spot before sympathizers could come to their rescue them, DAILY POST reports. The driver of the Toyota Hilux was immediately arrested by the Police in Ozoro Division.